Evening in the Garden  

As the sun descends, embracing the rich earth,  
  
The flowers sway in harmony, petals in flight;  
  
Nature's soft symphony, a song of rebirth,  
  
Revealing the beauty hidden from sight.

- Charles Baudelaire

- Charles Baudelaire
